headline: Crypto Revolution On Hold: SEC Pushes Franklin Templeton’s Bitcoin-Ethereum ETF Decision to 2025
summary: The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) has again delayed its decision on Franklin Templeton’s proposed Crypto Index ETF, setting a new deadline for Jan. 6, 2025.
